IMAPAccount fastmail
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port 993
User knowshank@fastmail.com
# FIXME: switch to authinfo.gpg
PassCmd "cat ~/.mbsync-fastmail"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

# local storage
MaildirStore fastmail-local
Path ~/Maildir/
Inbox ~/Maildir/INBOX
# The SubFolders option allows to represent all
# IMAP folders as local subfolders
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel fastmail
Far :fastmail-remote:
Near :fastmail-local:
Patterns *
Expunge None
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
Create Near
SyncState *